<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Give — Pitt Stop Ministries</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/donations.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/nav.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/footer.css">
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('partials/nav') %>

    <main id="body-main">
        <section id="section-h1" class="reveal">
            <h1>Bringing God's People Back to the Kingdom</h1>
        </section>

        <section id="section-h2" class="reveal">
            <p>God is not asking you do something you can do.</p>
            <p>He's asking you to be a part of something <span class="accent">HE</span> wants to do through you.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="btn-section" class="reveal">
            <h3>Give unto good ground, <br/> for it is <span style="font-weight: bold;">HE</span> that does the work.</h3>
            <p class="give-cadence">Give once, or give every month.</p>
            <button class="tithely-give-button" data-form="5d31f4b3-d682-418d-a663-cc76b7a8714f">Give</button>
            <p class="give-trust">Secure giving powered by Tithe.ly.</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script src="https://static.tithely.com/give/give.js" defer></script>
    <script src="/js/nav.js" defer></script>
    <script src="/js/donations.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>
